										</svg>
										<span class="ml-3 text-sm text-gray-700">Tire Shine</span>
									</li>
									<li class="flex items-start">
										<svg class="flex-shrink-0 h-5 w-5 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
